Pentatonix, a popular American acapella group,  just released the visual for Where Are You Christmas. The song is sure to make you feel the holiday cheer. Where Are You Christmas is part of the Pentatonix’s holiday album-Christmas  Is Here. Read More: Five Classic Christmas Carols  Kirstin Maldonado (Soprano singer), Mitch Grassi(Tenor singer), Scott Hoying(Baritone singer), Kevin Olusola(beat box) and Matt Sallee(Bass singer) are members of Pentatonix.